headline: Parnassus Growth Equity Fund Sold Akamai Technologies (AKAM) in Q3
summary: Parnassus Investments, an investment management company, released the “Parnassus Growth Equity Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Datadog (NASDAQ:DDOG) Vs The Rest Of The Software Development Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how software development stocks fared in Q3, starting with Datadog (NASDAQ:DDOG).
